==================
UPGRADING MWCHAT
==================

This document contains instructions for upgrading the MWChat
software on your system.

For information on the capabilities and features of MWChat, see
the file README in the docs/ directory of the MWChat
distribution.


UPGRADING MWChat
----------------

To upgrade MWChat, please download the latest release and follow the
instructions in the INSTALL file. Application Index can only upgrade
your serial number. Once you've installed the new release, go to the
license page (http://yourhost.com/mwchat/license.php) and there will
a link provided if you want to upgrade. Appindex will provide you with
your newly upgraded serial number. Enter that new serial number into the
the license page and your good to go.


Please see the INSTALL file if you need further support.
